OL,3,CStolen vehicles seized as part of pre-
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair operations
OL,6,FFour vehicles police say were stolen
OL,7,Fhave been seized as part of operations
OL,8,Faround Appleby Horse Fair, which runs
OL,9,Ffrom Thursday June 4 to Wednesday June
OL,10,F10.
OL,12,FA car, two horse boxes and a wood-
OL,13,Fchipper were found on Saturday May 30,
OL,14,Fand seized by officers working with
OL,15,Fthe National Stolen Vehicle team.
OL,17,FDetective Superintendent Dan St
OL,18,FQuintin, Gold Commander for Appleby
OL,19,FHorse Fair, said, "We make no
OL,20,Fapologies for targeting criminality as
OL,21,Fpart of this operation."
OL,26,@{D@SOU
