OL,3,CStolen vehicles seized as part of pre-
OL,4,CAppleby Horse Fair operations
OL,6,FHe continued, "Many of those attending
OL,7,Fthe Fair are law abiding citizens;
OL,8,Fhowever, we will not hesitate to take
OL,9,Faction where we find vehicles to be
OL,10,Fstolen."
OL,12,FHe says Appleby Horse Fair is the
OL,13,FConstabulary's largest annual policing
OL,14,Foperation, adding, "the public can
OL,15,Fexpect officers to carry out necessary
OL,16,Fchecks and act where they see
OL,17,Foffences, without fear or favour and
OL,18,Fregardless of which community the
OL,19,Findividual belongs to."
